Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.76,0:22:24.37,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Let's Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:28.01,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.50,0:22:28.01,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:31.54,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:31.54,edc,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:35.09,edj,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}Oh!
